CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776906184
OL,3,CUrgent action on oil and gas
OL,4,Cdecommissioning could create 25,000
OL,5,Cjobs ` report
OL,7,FA think tank has called for "urgent
OL,8,Faction" to ensure oil and gas
OL,9,Fcompanies decommission old North Sea
OL,10,Finfrastructure, saying doing so could
OL,11,Fcreate up to 25,000 jobs and deliver a
OL,12,F#15 billion economic boost.
OL,14,FA report by Redwater Insights found
OL,15,FGovernment action to guarantee
OL,16,Foperators clean up ageing
OL,17,Finfrastructure could also provide a
OL,18,F"critical skills bridge" for 15,000
OL,19,Fskilled workers facing an unemployment
OL,20,F"cliff edge" as the North Sea basin
OL,21,Fcontinues to decline.
OL,26,@oD@]OUpD@GO]zD@AOUzD@XO]|D@AOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776906184
OL,3,CUrgent action on oil and gas
OL,4,Cdecommissioning could create 25,000
OL,5,Cjobs ` report
OL,7,FTo achieve this, Redwater said the
OL,8,FNorth Sea Transition Authority ` which
OL,9,Fregulates the sector ` needs increased
OL,10,Fpowers to impose binding deadlines on
OL,11,Foperators around the decommissioning
OL,12,Fof infrastructure.
OL,14,FIt said currently regulators are
OL,15,F"regularly" approving requests to
OL,16,Fdelay removal of infrastructure,
OL,17,Fdespite some 500 oil and gas wells
OL,18,Falready being overdue for
OL,19,Fdecommissioning, and a further 1,700
OL,20,Fdue to be plugged in the next six
OL,21,Fyears.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776906184
OL,3,CUrgent action on oil and gas
OL,4,Cdecommissioning could create 25,000
OL,5,Cjobs ` report
OL,7,FThe body also called for operators to
OL,8,Fbe required to pre-fund some
OL,9,Fdecommissioning costs, and for more
OL,10,Fsupport to be given to workers
OL,11,Ftransitioning from oil and gas
OL,12,Fproduction to decommissioning roles.
OL,14,FRedwater Insights director of legal
OL,15,FSophie Marjanac said: "When operators
OL,16,Fdelay their clean up responsibilities,
OL,17,Fthis creates further uncertainty for
OL,18,Fworkers and their communities.
OL,26,@wD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776906184
OL,3,CUrgent action on oil and gas
OL,4,Cdecommissioning could create 25,000
OL,5,Cjobs ` report
OL,7,F"Proper decommissioning will provide a
OL,8,Fskills bridge for current oil and gas
OL,9,Fworkers and create new jobs along the
OL,10,Feast coast of the UK, from Aberdeen to
OL,11,FGreat Yarmouth.
OL,13,F"We need urgent action to avoid a
OL,14,Fdisaster for jobs, communities and the
OL,15,FUK economy.
OL,17,F"There are more than 500 oil and gas
OL,18,Fwells currently overdue for plugging
OL,19,Fand abandonment in the North Sea, with
OL,20,Fhundreds more expected to reach end-of-
OL,21,Flife in the next few years.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776906184
OL,3,CUrgent action on oil and gas
OL,4,Cdecommissioning could create 25,000
OL,5,Cjobs ` report
OL,7,F"Overly flexible regulation means
OL,8,Foperators are kicking the
OL,9,Fdecommissioning can down the road. But
OL,10,Fdelaying too much longer runs the risk
OL,11,Fof ballooning costs and highly skilled
OL,12,Fworkers leaving the industry."
OL,14,FThe report, entitled After The oil:
OL,15,FJobs And economic Impacts From UK
OL,16,FOffshore Decommissioning, calculated
OL,17,Fthat timely decommissioning could
OL,18,Fattract #25.6 billion of investment
OL,19,Ffrom operators.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776906184
OL,3,CUrgent action on oil and gas
OL,4,Cdecommissioning could create 25,000
OL,5,Cjobs ` report
OL,7,FIt said this would generate nearly #7
OL,8,Fbillion in direct economic benefit to
OL,9,Fthe UK, plus a further #9 billion in
OL,10,Findirect and "induced" gross value
OL,11,Fadded.
OL,13,FHowever it warned there is only a
OL,14,Fshort window to avoid delays causing
OL,15,F"potentially disastrous" impacts for
OL,16,FUK jobs and regional economies.
OL,26,@rD@NOUrD@VO]wD@AOUwD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776906184
OL,3,CUrgent action on oil and gas
OL,4,Cdecommissioning could create 25,000
OL,5,Cjobs ` report
OL,7,FThe report found oil well degradation
OL,8,Fand deterioration of structures are
OL,9,Fexpected to significantly increase the
OL,10,Fcost of repair and removal work ` and
OL,11,Fthat this would be exacerbated by
OL,12,Fworkers retiring or leaving the sector.
OL,14,FMs Marjanac went on: "The Treasury
OL,15,Fcould face a significant challenge if
OL,16,Fcost blowouts cause companies to fail
OL,17,Fand decommissioning liabilities fall
OL,18,Fto taxpayers.
OL,26,@vD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776906184
OL,3,CUrgent action on oil and gas
OL,4,Cdecommissioning could create 25,000
OL,5,Cjobs ` report
OL,7,F"Meanwhile, regional communities risk
OL,8,Fbeing hit harder if the only workers
OL,9,Fskilled enough to decommission old
OL,10,Fassets have had to leave the industry
OL,11,Fbecause of continued delays.
OL,13,F"There is a fast closing window for
OL,14,Fproper decommissioning.
OL,16,F"We need urgent action from
OL,17,FGovernment, regulators and most
OL,18,Fimportantly from operators who are
OL,19,Flegally obliged to ensure their wells
OL,20,Fare cleaned up properly."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOU|D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776906184
OL,3,CUrgent action on oil and gas
OL,4,Cdecommissioning could create 25,000
OL,5,Cjobs ` report
OL,7,FLang Banks, director of WWF Scotland,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Having earned hundreds of
OL,9,Fmillions of pounds in profit from
OL,10,Fextracting fossil fuels from under the
OL,11,FNorth Sea, it is only right that oil
OL,12,Fand gas companies clean up after
OL,13,Fthemselves.
OL,15,F"Unnecessarily delaying the
OL,16,Fdecommissioning of oil and gas
OL,17,Ffacilities leaves our marine
OL,18,Fenvironment at risk of harm and
OL,19,Fundermines efforts to create skilled
OL,20,Fjobs and support coastal communities."
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@AOU|D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
